&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/LATAM-LIMA-CENTRAL-OFFER-LOGO1.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-4258&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/LATAM-LIMA-CENTRAL-OFFER-LOGO1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;LATAM- LIMA- CENTRAL- OFFER- LOGO1&quot; width=&quot;65&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/MEDIA-2016-W50B-LOGO-sized.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-14488&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/MEDIA-2016-W50B-LOGO-sized.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;50Best_2015_logo&quot; width=&quot;50&quot; height=&quot;88&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/MEDIA-W50B-2015-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-10476&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/MEDIA-W50B-2015-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;MEDIA- W50B 2015 LOGO&quot; width=&quot;46&quot; height=&quot;83&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.theworlds50best.com/latinamerica/en/The-List/1-10/central.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-5452&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/MEDIA-2014-LATAM-50-BEST-LOGO-SMALL.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;MEDIA- 2014 LATAM 50 BEST LOGO- SMALL&quot; width=&quot;50&quot; height=&quot;83&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/MEDIA-LA50B-2015-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone wp-image-10474&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/MEDIA-LA50B-2015-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;MEDIA- LA50B- 2015- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;45&quot; height=&quot;82&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With globe-trotting credentials from culinary school, apprenticeships and early career work experience, the cuisine of Chef Virgilio Martinez is an exciting experience where Peruvian products prevail with hints of influence from afar. Central, set in a stylish, contemporary room with a glass wall looking into the active kitchen has earned its place&nbsp;at &lt;strong&gt;#1 on the&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2015 Latin America&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants, 2&lt;/strong&gt;016&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;World&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants #4&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;and &lt;strong&gt;Summum Awards &lt;/strong&gt;top restaurant in Peru&lt;strong&gt;. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please e-mail your reservation request to Central&rsquo;s&nbsp;Reservations Manager&nbsp;Stefan&iacute;a Gonzales&nbsp;at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:sgonzalez@centralrestaurante.com.pe&quot;&gt;sgonzalez@centralrestaurante.com.pe&lt;/a&gt;.&nbsp;Please include &amp;#8216;Diners Club Reservation Request&amp;#8217; in the subject title.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Please provide your name, the date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Booking requirements &ndash; No credit card required for booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Food allergies &ndash; Central&rsquo;s ingredients are indigenous to Peru and can sometimes contain elements such as nuts. Please advise of any food allergies prior to confirming your reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: As a courtesy, Central asks for 24 hour cancellation notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advance booking recommendation: Central&nbsp;requires&nbsp;booking&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;at least 90 days&nbsp;in advance&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservation&nbsp;office is open Monday-Friday from 9:00 to 18:00. Email received outside of those hours will be responded to&nbsp;within 3 business days.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must use your Diners Club Card for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offer is good for up to 5 guests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Menu is priced at 266 soles (price does&nbsp;&lt;u&gt;not&lt;/u&gt;&nbsp;include beverages) but may change due to market availability. Prices to be confirmed at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bookings must be made at least 3 months prior to the desired reservation date.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preferred reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Chef table visit and various tours based on availability of chefs on the evening of dining.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

